Summary: Black figure, no lights, cross pattern like airplane,
divs: Sighting DetailsWalking home from local establishment, well lit sky, dark cross pattern like a plane only large enough to see a simple cross pattern in night sky. Watched for a minute, followed until out of sight, seemed to be flying at the speed of a normal passenger airplane. No lights.
